
Authentication module inspired by the restful_authentication plugin.

# dir structure:

  - app_root  
    - lib  
      - authentication            
        - user_model                - modules to be included in the user model
          + encryption.rb             + encryption utility methods
          + password.rb               + authentication by password
          + remember_token.rb         + authentication by a token stored in a cookie
          + session_token.rb          + authentication by a token and the user id stored in the session
        + auth_keys.rb              + parameters used to encrypt data
        + helpers.rb                + app helpers module
        + authentication.rb         + main module class
   